title: Ebro In The Morning - Desus And Mero Split + The Future Of Ebro, Laura, and Rosenberg
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/19/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the Desus and Mero Split, Rosenberg's Nutcracker experience, meeting Shooter McGavin, Kodak Black, and so much more!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
